rows.label: tlk70000014_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Another weird customer has been
coming around lately. This one's a
pretty woman, but still...

rows.label: tlk70000014_04_msg0002
rows.name:
She asks me to recommend feminine
clothes and stuff, "so she can be pretty
like me". But I sell pictures, not clothes!

rows.label: tlk70000014_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I told her I thought she was beautiful
the way she was, but she just said that
she wanted to dial it up to 11.

rows.label: tlk70000014_04_msg0004
rows.name:
It seems like there has to be a reason
behind it...but I'm not really sure how
appropriate it is for me to ask, though.

rows.label: tlk70000014_04_msg0005
rows.name:
...No, come on, Sarah! I promised
myself I'd be better about being honest
with people!

rows.label: tlk70000014_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Maybe I'll try talking to her again the
next time she comes in. If she ends up
being nice, I can introduce her to you!
